The,Scripto,API,connects,the,Axeda,Custom,Object,scripting,engine,and,a,Web,Service,client,Using,Scripto,users,can,code,a,script,in,the,Groovy,language,using,the,Axeda,SDK,and,potentially,mashing,up,results,from,other,systems,all,within,the,platform,and,expose,the,script,to,an,external,consumer,via,a,single,REST,based,Web,Service,operation,The,Axeda,Platform,enables,users,to,build,enterprise,M,M,applications,for,connected,products,both,wired,and,wireless,API,responses,can,be,formatted,in,XML,JSON,or,CSV